      <title>埃里安称美国经济放缓，美联储应考虑 7 月降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-28/el-erian-says-us-slowing-fed-should-consider-july-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社观点撰稿人穆罕默德·埃利安在彭博电视台表示，美国经济放缓的速度比美联储预期的要快。埃利安的观点仅代表他个人观点。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-28/el-erian-says-us-slowing-fed-should-consider-july-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 13:30:51 GMT</pubDate>
