      <title>Milei 称立法胜利为货币政策调整铺平道路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/milei-says-legislative-win-paves-way-for-monetary-policy-pivot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱周五表示，他的政府将改变货币政策框架，这是他首次取得重大立法胜利，确保了其具有里程碑意义的经济改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/milei-says-legislative-win-paves-way-for-monetary-policy-pivot</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 13:28:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储首选的潜在通胀指标放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-28/fed-s-preferred-measure-of-underlying-inflation-slows-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[核心个人消费支出价格指数较上月上涨 0.1%。这是六个月以来最小的涨幅。按未四舍五入计算，该指数仅上涨 0.08%，为 2020 年 11 月以来的最低水平。Mike McKee 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-28/fed-s-preferred-measure-of-underlying-inflation-slows-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 13:21:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储戴利称最新数据显示货币政策正在发挥作用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/fed-s-daly-says-latest-data-show-monetary-policy-is-working</link>
      <description><![CDATA[旧金山联邦储备银行行长玛丽戴利表示，周五公布的通胀数据表明货币政策正在发挥作用，但现在判断何时降低借贷成本还为时过早。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/fed-s-daly-says-latest-data-show-monetary-policy-is-working</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 13:13:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
